OL,3,CInfected blood: 'They murdered my
OL,4,Cfamily and they murdered many more'
OL,6,FA man who lost his mum, dad and sister
OL,7,Faged just three as a result of the
OL,8,Finfected blood scandal says he
OL,9,Fbelieves "someone should go to prison"
OL,10,Ffor the failings.
OL,12,FSam Rushby after his haemophiliac
OL,13,Ffather Gary received contaminated
OL,14,FFactor 8, a clotting agent derived
OL,15,Ffrom blood plasma, 30 years ago.
OL,17,FHe had no idea it had made him HIV
OL,18,Fpositive, and then unknowingly passed
OL,19,Fit to his wife Lesley and their new
OL,20,Fbaby girl Abbey.
