OL,3,CInfected blood: 'They murdered my
OL,4,Cfamily and they murdered many more'
OL,6,FThe youngster died aged just four-
OL,7,Fmonths-old, while her 23-year-old
OL,8,Fmother Lesley died in 1994, followed
OL,9,Fby Gary in 1995 at the age of 34. All
OL,10,Fhad AIDS related conditions.
OL,12,FSam said: "They knew what they were
OL,13,Fdoing, they murdered my family and
OL,14,Fthey murdered many more families too."
OL,16,FHis comments come following the
OL,17,Frelease of the public inquiry report
OL,18,Finto the scandal, which claimed
OL,19,Fthousands of lives, saying it was "no
OL,20,Faccident".
