OL,6,FIt found the risks were "well-known"
OL,7,Fdecades before the infected blood
OL,8,Fproducts were used on patients in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FReport author Sir Brian Langstaff
OL,12,Fconcluded "the chief responsibility
OL,13,Ffor the failings lied with successive
OL,14,Fgovernments", and that they "showed
OL,15,Flittle interest in finding the truth".
