OL,3,CInfected blood: 'They murdered my
OL,4,Cfamily and they murdered many more'
OL,6,F"Basically my whole family were torn
OL,7,Faway from me," Sam said. "(Dad)
OL,8,Fwatched his four-month-old daughter
OL,9,Fdie, then he watched his wife die and
OL,10,Fhe knew he was going to die. It's just
OL,11,Fhorrific."
OL,13,FSam was in London with his wife
OL,14,FRebecca to hear the results of the
OL,15,Finquiry into the scandal.
