OL,3,CInfected blood: 'They murdered my
OL,4,Cfamily and they murdered many more'
OL,6,F"Finally the truth is out," he said.
OL,7,F"We've been saying it for years, the
OL,8,Fhealth service, the Government, the
OL,9,FDoctors everybody they all knew and
OL,10,Fthey were all warned that it was
OL,11,Finfected and still they carried on
OL,12,Fthey didn't care and then they tried
OL,13,Fto cover it up and now the truth is
OL,14,Fout."
OL,16,FThe inquiry was told Factor 8 was
OL,17,Fconsidered a wonder drug in the 1970s
OL,18,Fbecause it allowed haemophiliacs to
OL,19,Finject themselves at home rather than
OL,20,Fgoing to hospital.
