OL,3,CInfected blood: 'They murdered my
OL,4,Cfamily and they murdered many more'
OL,6,FThe plasma-derived product helped
OL,7,Fclotting and curbed the bleeding from
OL,8,Fminor injuries that haemophiliacs
OL,9,Fexperienced.
OL,11,FBut demand was so high that the NHS
OL,12,Fhad to turn to drug companies in the
OL,13,FUnited States for supplies. In the US
OL,14,Fdonations were paid for, attracting
OL,15,Fthose desperate for cash.
OL,17,FDrug addicts, sex workers and
OL,18,Falcoholics were among those regularly
OL,19,Fgiving blood, increasing the risk of
OL,20,Fthat supply being infected.
