OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has issued
OL,7,Fan apology following the publication
OL,8,Fof the report, with ministers thought
OL,9,Fto be preparing to set out the
OL,10,Fcompensation package - expected to be
OL,11,Fmore than #10 billion.
OL,13,FBut Sam said it is not enough, instead
OL,14,Fbelieving criminal charges should be
OL,15,Fbrought.
OL,17,F"It is not good enough the evidence
OL,18,Fhas to go to the CPS, people have to
OL,19,Fbe held accountable and someone should
OL,20,Fgo to prison for this."
